Title: Deformed W-algebras as Symmetries of Generalized Integrable Hierarchies

Authors: C.R. Fern\'andez-Pousa, M.V. Gallas, J.L. Miramontes and J. S\'anchez

Guill\'enComments: Plain TeX file

A unified description of the relationship between the Hamiltonian structureof a large class of integrable hierarchies of equations and W-algebras isdiscussed. The main result is an explicit formula showing that the former canbe understood as a deformation of the latter.